message.content: cs.HC, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.COG - The paper focuses on the cognitive aspects of design and the construction of representations, which are relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also discusses the organization and strategies of design, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SD) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper explores the nature of design and its potential specificity in HCI design, which relates to cognitive science (cs.COG).
